.Ed
.Pp
The
.Fn pkey_size
method returns the key size in bytes.
It is called by
.Xr EVP_PKEY_size 3 .
.Pp
The
.Fn pkey_bits
method returns the key size in bits.
It is called by
.Xr EVP_PKEY_bits 3 .
